Noughts & Crosses

Written in PHP 7.1
Db used in a MariaDB provided by docker.

Running:

php noughtscrosses.php will display help text

Usage: noughtscrosses.php [ACTION]
    Actions:
        Results - Output all-time results from all games ever.
        Calculate - Calculate results from round of games provided via STDIN


Database has only one table, and it's sql is in the nac.sql file

There is a option of loading input data from file, not from STDIN:

php noughtscrosses.php calculate < data.txt

That's all!